        "words": "聽她訴說喔。",
        "unit_id": 192011
    },
    {
        "type": "dialogue",
        "name": "美空",
        "words": "因為厄莉絲大人她",
        "unit_id": 192011,
        "voice": "vo_adv_2114010_068"
    },
    {
        "type": "dialogue",
        "name": "美空",
        "words": "好像不喜歡動用洗腦之類的手段……",
        "unit_id": 192011
    },
    {
        "type": "dialogue",
        "name": "美空",
        "words": "\n所以到頭來，",
        "unit_id": 192011
    },
    {
        "type": "dialogue",
        "name": "美空",
        "words": "\n究竟要選擇誰，",
        "unit_id": 192011
    },
    {
        "type": "dialogue",
        "name": "美空",
        "words": "決定權還是在你手上。",
